		<item>
		<title>Fastest Flax Seed Farms &#8211; Heart of Thorns and Path of Fire</title>
		<link>/flax-seed-farm/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Matt]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Fri, 21 Aug 2020 08:42:48 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Guides]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Guild Wars 2]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://marvweb.com/?p=735</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[Learn the best places to quickly and efficiently farm Flax Seeds in Guild Wars 2. This guide includes the best spots from HoT and PoF.]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p><a href="https://wiki.guildwars2.com/wiki/Pile_of_Flax_Seeds">Flax Seeds</a> continue to be in great demand due to them being an ingredient in <strong><a href="https://wiki.guildwars2.com/wiki/Vial_of_Linseed_Oil">Linseed Oil</a>,</strong> an item used in many recipes including Guild Hall upgrades. This guide will show you the best Flax Seed farm spots in Guild Wars 2 Heart of Thorns &amp; Path of Fire.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Flax Seed Farm Spots</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Flax with no fuss: <a href="https://wiki.guildwars2.com/wiki/Jaka_Itzel">Jaka Itzel Waypoint</a> (Verdant Brink)</h3>



<figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter size-large"><a href="/wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-verdant-map.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="/wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-verdant-map-1024x576.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-9075" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-verdant-map-1024x576.jpg 1024w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-verdant-map-300x169.jpg 300w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-verdant-map-768x432.jpg 768w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-verdant-map-1536x864.jpg 1536w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-verdant-map.jpg 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"><em><a href="https://wiki.guildwars2.com/wiki/Jaka_Itzel">Jaka Itzel Waypoint</a> &#8211; Verdant Brink</em></figcaption></figure>



<p>This is the best place to farm Flax Seeds. There are enemies that attack the location every now and then, but the NPCs will usually stop them from reaching the farm, freeing you to focus on farming and not fighting. The nodes are also very condensed, making the farm quick. </p>



<p>I suggest parking your alts here and quickly picking up the 7-8 flax nodes every day. Unless you&#8217;re looking to maximize your daily return on Flax, parking your alts here and gathering daily will get you plenty of Flax with minimal time investment.</p>



<p>To reach this Flax farm location, take the Jaka Itzel waypoint in Verdant Brink. Jump over the edge and glide all the way down, slightly north-east of the waypoint.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter size-large"><a href="/wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-verdant-wp.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="/wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-verdant-wp-1024x576.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-9076" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-verdant-wp-1024x576.jpg 1024w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-verdant-wp-300x169.jpg 300w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-verdant-wp-768x432.jpg 768w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-verdant-wp-1536x864.jpg 1536w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-verdant-wp.jpg 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"><em>Jump down from Jaka Itzel Waypoint</em></figcaption></figure>



<figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter size-large"><a href="/wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-verdant-glide.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="/wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-verdant-glide-1024x576.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-9074" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-verdant-glide-1024x576.jpg 1024w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-verdant-glide-300x169.jpg 300w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-verdant-glide-768x432.jpg 768w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-verdant-glide-1536x864.jpg 1536w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-verdant-glide.jpg 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"><em>Glide just to the right of the updraft</em></figcaption></figure>



<hr class="wp-block-separator has-text-color has-vivid-purple-color has-css-opacity has-vivid-purple-background-color has-background"/>



<script async="" src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-4537180102637521" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
<ins class="adsbygoogle" style="display:block; text-align:center;" data-ad-layout="in-article" data-ad-format="fluid" data-ad-client="ca-pub-4537180102637521" data-ad-slot="5280630734"></ins>
<script>
     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});
</script>



<hr class="wp-block-separator has-text-color has-background" style="background-color:#663399;color:#663399"/>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">A little out of the way: <a href="https://wiki.guildwars2.com/wiki/Pride_of_the_Pact">Soulkeeper&#8217;s Airship Waypoint</a> (Bloodstone Fen)</h3>



<figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter size-large"><a href="/wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-bloodstone-map.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="/wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-bloodstone-map-1024x576.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-9059" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-bloodstone-map-1024x576.jpg 1024w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-bloodstone-map-300x169.jpg 300w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-bloodstone-map-768x432.jpg 768w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-bloodstone-map-1536x864.jpg 1536w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-bloodstone-map.jpg 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"><em><a href="https://wiki.guildwars2.com/wiki/Pride_of_the_Pact">Airship Waypoint</a> &#8211; Bloodstone Fen</em></figcaption></figure>



<p>This Flax Seed farm is a bit spread out, but still pretty efficient. There are 8 Flax nodes spread out on three floating islands in Bloodstone Fen. There are a few enemies near these nodes, but they won&#8217;t pose much of a threat. Getting to these location will require at least the <strong>Updraft </strong>mastery. <strong>Ley Line Gliding</strong> can make this run even faster, but is not needed. This also takes you to the diving goggles that are a great place to farm <strong>Unbound Magic</strong> daily.</p>



<p>There are three floating islands that contain Flax nodes. Aim for the two on the northern part of the map first. From Soulkeeper&#8217;s Airship Waypoint, use the updrafts (or the Ley Line if you have the mastery) to make your way to the small grass covered floating islands to the north-east of the airship. From there, you can glide down to the top of the large grassy island. Once you harvest the flax nodes there, drop off the northern edge of the island to find the last two nodes.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter size-large"><a href="/wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-bloodstone-airship.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="/wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-bloodstone-airship-1024x576.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-9057" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-bloodstone-airship-1024x576.jpg 1024w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-bloodstone-airship-300x169.jpg 300w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-bloodstone-airship-768x432.jpg 768w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-bloodstone-airship-1536x864.jpg 1536w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-bloodstone-airship.jpg 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"><em>The three islands with Flax nodes &#8211; Updraft or Ley Line glide to them</em></figcaption></figure>



<figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter size-large"><a href="/wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-bloodstone-flax.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="/wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-bloodstone-flax-1024x576.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-9058" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-bloodstone-flax-1024x576.jpg 1024w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-bloodstone-flax-300x169.jpg 300w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-bloodstone-flax-768x432.jpg 768w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-bloodstone-flax-1536x864.jpg 1536w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-bloodstone-flax.jpg 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"><em>Three nodes on the two small islands, five nodes on the big island</em></figcaption></figure>



<hr class="wp-block-separator has-text-color has-vivid-purple-color has-css-opacity has-vivid-purple-background-color has-background"/>



<script async="" src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-4537180102637521" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
<ins class="adsbygoogle" style="display:block; text-align:center;" data-ad-layout="in-article" data-ad-format="fluid" data-ad-client="ca-pub-4537180102637521" data-ad-slot="5280630734"></ins>
<script>
     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});
</script>



<hr class="wp-block-separator has-text-color has-background" style="background-color:#663399;color:#663399"/>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">An annoying defender: <a href="https://wiki.guildwars2.com/wiki/Heathen%27s_Hold">Heathen&#8217;s Hold Waypoint</a> (Draconis Mons)</h3>



<figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter size-large"><a href="/wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-draconis-map.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="/wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-draconis-map-1024x576.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-9063" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-draconis-map-1024x576.jpg 1024w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-draconis-map-300x169.jpg 300w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-draconis-map-768x432.jpg 768w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-draconis-map-1536x864.jpg 1536w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-draconis-map.jpg 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"><em><a href="https://wiki.guildwars2.com/wiki/Heathen%27s_Hold">Heathen&#8217;s Hold Waypoint</a> &#8211; Draconis Mons</em></figcaption></figure>



<p>This spot has a good amount of Flax that is relatively compact. However, there are a few enemies that may interrupt your harvest. The main issue here is that a group event boss can spawn in this area, making it difficult to collect the nodes until it is defeated.</p>



<p>To get to this spot, go to the Heathen&#8217;s Hold Waypoint in Draconis Mons. From there, jump off the western cliff where the three unbound magic nodes are. Fall straight through the three unbound magics and glide to the lower ledge sticking out. From this cliff, enter the cave back to the east. The farm location is at the end of the right path of the cave.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter size-large"><a href="/wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-draconis-wp.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="/wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-draconis-wp-1024x576.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-9064" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-draconis-wp-1024x576.jpg 1024w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-draconis-wp-300x169.jpg 300w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-draconis-wp-768x432.jpg 768w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-draconis-wp-1536x864.jpg 1536w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-draconis-wp.jpg 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"><em>From Heathen&#8217;s Hold Waypoint, drop off the cliff at the unbound magic nodes</em></figcaption></figure>



