<h3 class="wp-block-heading">A tough fight: <a href="https://wiki.guildwars2.com/wiki/Order_of_Whispers_Camp">Order of Whispers Camp Waypoint</a> (Tangled Depths)</h3>



<figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter size-large"><a href="/wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-tangled-map.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="/wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-tangled-map-1024x576.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-9072" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-tangled-map-1024x576.jpg 1024w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-tangled-map-300x169.jpg 300w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-tangled-map-768x432.jpg 768w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-tangled-map-1536x864.jpg 1536w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-tangled-map.jpg 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"><em><a href="https://wiki.guildwars2.com/wiki/Order_of_Whispers_Camp">Order of Whispers Camp Waypoint</a> OR Ogre Camp Waypoint &#8211; Tangled Depths</em></figcaption></figure>



<p>This group of Flax nodes is protected by some tough enemies. It is also a bit of a pain to get to. You will need the <strong>Updraft</strong> mastery or a <strong>Springer</strong> mount to make it to this spot.</p>



<p>From Order of Whispers Camp Waypoint in Tangled Depths, head toward the open area full of updrafts. Either use those updrafts or your Springer to make it to the south-eastern upper ledge. If using your Springer, climb up the eastern wall toward the Vista. If using updrafts, start at the southern wall. Stay to the left at the fork to make it to the open area with the flax. There are also two chests nearby that can be looted while you are here. </p>



<p>You can also reach this area by using your Springer from the Ogre Camp Waypoint, but the jumps are tough.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter size-large"><a href="/wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-tangled-wp.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="/wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-tangled-wp-1024x576.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-9073" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-tangled-wp-1024x576.jpg 1024w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-tangled-wp-300x169.jpg 300w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-tangled-wp-768x432.jpg 768w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-tangled-wp-1536x864.jpg 1536w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-tangled-wp.jpg 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"><em>The easier path &#8211; Order of Whispers Camp Waypoint</em></figcaption></figure>



