<h3 class="wp-block-heading">All over the place: <a href="https://wiki.guildwars2.com/wiki/Reclaimed_Chantry">Reclaimed Chantry Waypoint</a> (Jahai Bluffs)</h3>



<figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter size-large"><a href="/wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-jahai-map.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="/wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-jahai-map-1024x576.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-9067" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-jahai-map-1024x576.jpg 1024w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-jahai-map-300x169.jpg 300w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-jahai-map-768x432.jpg 768w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-jahai-map-1536x864.jpg 1536w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-jahai-map.jpg 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"><em><a href="https://wiki.guildwars2.com/wiki/Reclaimed_Chantry">Reclaimed Chantry Waypoint </a>&#8211; Jahai Bluffs</em></figcaption></figure>



<p>This &#8220;spot&#8221; is more of an area. There are multiple flax nodes to find in the Jungle Anomaly of Jahai Bluffs. Most of them are in the upper area of the jungle. To get to them, you will need a <strong>Springer </strong>or the <strong>Bouncing Mushrooms</strong> mastery. You&#8217;ll have to contend with Chakk, so the Chakk mastery is helpful but not necessary. </p>



<p>To get there from the Reclaimed Chantry Waypoint, head south and turn west. Go through the cave to the west. Continue heading west through the Branded area until you make it to the Jungle Anomaly. Once in the anomaly, use your Springer or the bouncing mushrooms to make it up to the higher area. There are flax nodes throughout this area.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter size-large"><a href="/wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-jahai-wp.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="/wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-jahai-wp-1024x576.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-9068" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-jahai-wp-1024x576.jpg 1024w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-jahai-wp-300x169.jpg 300w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-jahai-wp-768x432.jpg 768w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-jahai-wp-1536x864.jpg 1536w, /wp-content/uploads/flax-farm-jahai-wp.jpg 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"><em>Head toward the heart from the waypoint, then continue on to the cave</em></figcaption></figure>



